(1, 'ducchinhbk', '$P$BjhiD2sG6EcgXbv10BxbBBIMByNY.o1', 'ducchinhbk', 'ducchinhbk@gmail.com', '', '2015-01-03 15:08:26', '', 0, 'ducchinhbk', 'We comprises a skilled and professional team of internet marketers with 10 years of experience in developing integrated tools in optimizing social media sites. We assure clients with an improved websites for their effective internet marketing efforts. By availing the company’s services, there is a great chance for businesses online to become more recognizable on different social networks, which in return can increase your level of earnings to several times larger. We are also experts in design, seo optimization, facebook marketing, Facebook apps, Html, ....', 'upload/avatar/chinh.png', 'upload/cover/chinh.jpg', 'Everything come to you in the right moment! Be patient!', 'Bussiness man', 'Zotadi Global Corporation', 'Hồ Chí Minh', 'Tran Duc', 'Chinh', '', '', 1),
